      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MONTY ZOOMER (2) missed three back when beaten a head before going back-to-back in good fashion here, winning over 1400m just last week. Back up to this trip is no issue as he scored as favourite here two back and the form out of that stacked up. Will take catching. PLEASE MIZTER (6) finished behind MONTY ZOOMER here a fortnight ago when fading out of contention after sitting on the speed. He has been better in his starts prior and Fiore now hops on board again. Can bounce back to winning ways. FEUDING (1) was just fair off a 65-day break last start and steps out to a better trip this time around. He's won 2/4 at this track and trip and Faithfull is a strike jockey for the Fernie barn. Can improve sharply. SNIPPERANDO (8) can improve on the fresh run.",
